  (Decision
    "Workspace gets an intent/ directory recording what the author explicitly said, organized by topic, distinct from documentation and reports. Each entry carries a terse rephrasing, verbatim quote with surrounding context, certainty marker, and timestamp. Migrates eventually to a persona-mind memory variant."
