    "Intent records use positional NOTA with kind-typed wrapping (Decision/Principle/Correction/Clarification/Constraint). Topic is the directory; sub-topic is the filename. Multiple records per file allowed when they're on the same sub-topic. Supersession is explicit — the agent detecting contradiction surfaces the prior verbatim+context+certainty inline before recording the override."
